<bibRefCitation id="1F604B7C2100FF94B266FBA88BE4FBE5" author="ASSING V" box="[793,948,1102,1124]" pageId="7" pageNumber="198" pagination="49 - 128" refId="ref8487" refString="ASSING V. (2012): A revision of East Palaearctic Lobrathium (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Bonn Zoological Bulletin 61 (1): 49 - 128." type="journal article" year="2012">ASSING (2012)</bibRefCitation>
. The above specimens from 
<collectingRegion id="B935F86F2100FF94B035FB8D89DBFB00" box="[330,395,1131,1153]" country="China" name="Gansu" pageId="7" pageNumber="198">Gansu</collectingRegion>
